	<h1 id="Task">Task#3: Mouse and Click Event</h1>
	<p>Show "On Mouse Over" when I mouse over the link; Show "On Mouse Out" when I mouse out the link;(do the same for Mouse Down, and Mouse Up) when Double Click,Show "On Double Click"</p>
	<a href="#" id="showMouse">Show Event Here</a>

	<!-- <a href="JavaScript:void(0)" id="makemealien" 
	  onmouseover="this.text='On Mouse Over'"
